            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/5df6e0261705deb19cfc26f239251c85_8463284565813192190.png",
                "id": "talent93243",
                "key": "蝎爪钳击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蝎爪钳击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。生成1张<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span>，随机置入我方牌库顶部2张牌之中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/86ad2f9a487b5e1fc7f14c6d3aebf17a_3654063000826339914.png",
                "id": "talent83218",
                "key": "蝎尾锥刺",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蝎尾锥刺"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>手牌中最多3张<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span>，在对方场上生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷锥陷阱</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/aebba01f5c8d920339645f679cd512aa_6474646957420346485.png",
                "id": "talent50254",
                "key": "雷锥散射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷锥散射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】回合结束时，生成2张<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span>，随机置入我方牌库顶部10张牌之中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/2f5fbc2acab943dc5e598980c758f964_7436948679753494232.png",
                "id": "talent59700",
                "key": "不朽亡骸·雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "不朽亡骸·雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">事件牌</span><br>随机舍弃1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌，生成1个我方出战角色类型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1张）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/c91f35411606350c7340492100653c9a_4921476133014501560.png",
                "id": "talent10454",
                "key": "噬骸能量块",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_1531766883888369224.png",
                "title": "噬骸能量块"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/a7f398e6632a554920f91b6563f341fa_4878813629788857357.png",
                "id": "talent77824",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span></strong></p><p>随机<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌，生成1个我方出战角色类型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1张）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷锥陷阱</span></strong></p><p>所在阵营的角色使用技能后：对所在阵营的出战角色造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>：初始为创建时所弃置的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span>张数。（最多叠加到3）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_6236758675876598852.png",
